description: Candy Box（CANDYBOX）which is called Candy Token (CANDY) before, is the sum of a candy token. Since the total amount of CANDY is one trillion, after the exchange at the ratio of 100 CANDY = 1 CANDYBOX, the upside total amount of CANDYBOX is 10 billion. Through this project, different project parties lock their respective candy to the same address and jointly issued and distribute them to users who support the project in various ways, such as airdrops and gifts. There are more than 30 kinds of tokens locked include ETH, PRS, XIN, etc which values nearly 10 million dollars.
name: Candy Box
